Package org.cloudsimplus.traces.azure

Class TracesStatisticsManager

java.lang.Object
org.cloudsimplus.traces.azure.TracesStatisticsManager
public class TracesStatisticsManager extends Object
A class for facilitating the statistics/traces collection by keeping all the measurements in a single place.
Since:
CloudSim Plus 7.3.2
Author:
Pavlos Maniotis
